{"tid":1656524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗爭妙法】成本小、效用大","createTime":"2019-10-15T15:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T15:34:08.000Z","uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"829eea765b32d35564848e7ed94e0c0d717c12c0","tid":1656524,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"轉頭硬物並不能令全副武裝的黑警懼怕<br />\n相反嘔心物，如「屎蛋、臭蛋」等&hellip;<br />\n更能令一般人退避和恐懼<br />\n相信會對黑警造成一定的心理壓力<br />\n若然有任何裝備受到染污<br />\n定必馬上想卸下惡臭的隨身裝備<br />\n從而進一步影響其他同袍心態<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（相信你都唔會坐響個周身屎臭嘅人旁邊）</span><br />\n<br />\n重點集中對付<br />\n「狗車」的門柄及窗邊這些必須經常接觸的位置<br />\n令嘔心物更容易散播開其他地方，冷氣入口位置（前方或車頂位置）<br />\n<br />\n「狗屋」的通風系統，如冷氣機、抽氣扇、鮮風入口位置<br />\n停車場、外牆、大門入口及窗亦可，目的令整幢建築物臭氣熏天！<br />\n<br />\n只要大家齊心，毎人自製10至20隻屎蛋<br />\n相信數量一定相當可觀<br />\n非常期待「屎蛋」如雨下的情境招呼黑警<br />\n和事後中招的黑警的狼狽表現<br />\n<br />\n噁心的臭蛋<br />\n<a href=\"https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felite0905.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F25928800&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=339cec3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800</a><br />\n<br />\n如何自製臭雞蛋（須時較長）<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikihow.com/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AD%E7%82%B8%E5%BC%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikihow.com%2F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2587%25AD%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BC%25B9&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=dc2ed481\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikihow.com/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AD%E7%82%B8%E5%BC%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n如何自製屎蛋（即成）<br />\n1. 在雞蛋頂端刺穿一個小洞<br />\n2. 用針筒抽出一半蛋液<br />\n3. 用針筒注入糞便混合<br />\n4. 最後用熱溶膠密封小洞<br />\n<br />\n最後送上一則伊索寓言《風和太陽》作為參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fg9e6yle.html&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f78a357d\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html</a>"},{"pid":"0b31e9f64ca20d051075c8a07727933758bfa2af","tid":1656524,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"69d048ffdd09f7da8fa44c7a449a4ec70bb41415","tid":1656524,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}